id=lan-killswitch
name=LAN Kill Switch
version=v1.1.0
versionCode=2
author=eiaydin
description=Tethering-aware VPN kill switch. Blocks hotspot / USB-tether / Wi-Fi-AP clients from reaching the internet whenever no tun* interface exists. Closes the gap that Android's built-in "Block connections without VPN" does NOT cover (it only filters the device's own apps, not forwarded tethering traffic). Toggle via Magisk Manager (requires reboot).
